{"tid":1666537,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清真寺代表稱特首及盧偉聰道歉 盧偉聰離開時無回應","createTime":"2019-10-21T04:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T05:38:07.000Z","uid":74778,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a062114365155e86904c2124e8e964dc858dc3c0","tid":1666537,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"清真寺代表稱特首及盧偉聰道歉 盧偉聰離開時無回應 <br />\n<br />\n警方昨日在尖沙咀彌敦道以水炮車驅散示威者時，清真寺被噴中，正門及鐵閘都被染藍。行政長官林鄭月娥與警務處處長盧偉聰上午11時許達到清真寺，與教長會面。會後盧偉聰被問到是否前來道歉、水炮車是否刻意射向清真寺等，他未有回應。清真寺代表Saeed Uddin 在會後說，林鄭月娥及盧偉聰有向他們道歉，承諾類似事件不會再發生。清真寺的代表就接受道歉，又說穆斯林團體在香港一向非常和平，昨日在清真寺亦沒有發生暴力事件，警方沒有理由前來破壞。清真寺代表又感謝市民和警方在事後協助清理，又說穆斯林是支持香港。<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-21 12:20:18<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/80315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F80315&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERc%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=2ba98907\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/80315</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721都wfc，射清真寺又做show洗場又出聲明又道歉！屌政府老母臭閪！！！！<br />\n<br />\n你老母閪你當香港人係乜撚野啊！！！<br />\n<br />\n洗彌敦道未！？洗深水埗未？！洗黃大仙廟未？！洗安老院未？！洗新城市未？！洗旺角未？！<br />\n血跡未洗你老母臭閪洗顏料？！你為顏料道歉？！！！？！！<br />\n</span></span></strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPZf6Ja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPZf6Ja.jpg&h=5ee3e3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iBOQa9Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiBOQa9Y.jpg&h=a7fd3b1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對住香港巿民: 警方做野跟程序，合理合法，有咩唔滿意打去投訴，會睇下點處理，係咁。<br />\n<br />\n721都唔洗道歉，加多句<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XyTTrt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XyTTrt.gif&h=1269165d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彌敦道唔見佢洗，旺角唔唔見佢洗，深水埗老人院唔見佢洗，黃大仙廟唔見佢洗，新城市唔見佢洗，<br />\n<br />\n話時話，黃大仙都算香港本土神仙，屌班狗洗d鬼佬神，都唔柒理黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港政府真係當本土巿民本土文化係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔割！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要CONNET！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要割同警割！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">cls政府完全當香港巿民係臭四！！！！<br />\n<br />\n出聲明！ 做show洗場！ 道歉！ 特首探望！24個鐘唔洗做齊！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n香港巿民訴求？？！5個月都未理過！！！！<br />\n<br />\n陳彥霖？！幾個星期提都唔撚提<br />\n<br />\n今次清真事件先最嬲！嬲在政府不為非不能！！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"316fed15b4859dd45e9b351b3d9d65ecae6b6d60","tid":1666537,"uid":172638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 21<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>12:30 醫民同行 醫護抗暴 靜坐行動</strong></span> <br />\n- 八間醫院<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>19:00 - 23:00 毋忘721 元朗恐襲三個月靜坐</strong></span><br />\n- 18區黨鐵站大堂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>#39mRunFor721 全港和理跑</strong></span><br />\n- [時間地點不限 跑步計時39分鐘]"},{"pid":"37f095876acc15b3d6963f5be002b74354ea24d1","tid":1666537,"uid":48948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04: